{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0Mzg2NzAzOTky", "number": 4048, "title": "Limit system ram to 4GB", "bodyText": "Might treat some symptoms of #3128, #3657, #3918, #3917, #3686, #3677\nOpenJDK assumes total system RAM of 128GB. Setting it to 4GB manually\nreduces the greediness of the JVM drastically.\nOnly after setting the MaxRAM to 1.5GB it finally went into a heap space error. 2GB work fine on my machine.\nProposed strategy: do a full release test with this, see how it goes.\nThis find is courtesy of @ghubstan #3918 (comment)", "createdAt": "2020-03-11T13:55:04Z", "url": "https://github.com/bisq-network/bisq/pull/4048", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "96934d910745537c165a560864ef9cd6e83710c4"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-03-12T09:30:43Z", "author": {"login": "freimair"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 7, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcMnBbjAH2gAyMzg2NzAzOTkyOmRjN2E5MDRhN2ZhY2Y1NDBmZGU2NWY3NjBiNDNkODQyYjgzYTkyZDM=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcM4UYRgFqTM3MzM5NDQxOQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "dc7a904a7facf540fde65f760b43d842b83a92d3", "author": {"user": {"login": "freimair", "name": "Florian Reimair"}}, "url": "https://github.com/bisq-network/bisq/commit/dc7a904a7facf540fde65f760b43d842b83a92d3", "committedDate": "2020-03-11T13:21:02Z", "message": "Limits system ram to 4GB\n\nOpenJDK assumes total system RAM of 128GB. Setting it to 4GB manually\nreduces the greediness of the JVM drastically."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzcyODU3MTgy", "url": "https://github.com/bisq-network/bisq/pull/4048#pullrequestreview-372857182", "createdAt": "2020-03-11T15:16:33Z", "commit": {"oid": "4f234dbd60f6374d70dd3005dbd4e84c0637cbb8"}, "state": "CHANGES_REQUESTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 0, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": null, "endCursor": null, "hasNextPage": false, "hasPr